Former DirecTV CEO talks negotiating NFL Sunday Ticket|http://www.cnbc.com/netnet|http://www.cnbc.com/video/2017/10/25/former-directv-ceo-talks-negotiating-nfl-sunday-ticket.html||2017-10-25|||Former DirecTV CEO talks negotiating NFL Sunday Ticket

5:37 PM ET Wed, 25 Oct 2017

At CNBC’s NetNet Summit at the NYSE, Michael White, former DirecTV CEO and PepsiCO CFO, describes the arguments behind the company’s negotiations with the NFL and Roger Goodell in obtaining NFL Sunday Ticket.
